Name: Princesses Never Lose!
About the game: On the western part of the Stivale Peninsula lies the small kingdom of Tolinia. Their princess, Erica, senses the danger to her kingdom, as the peninsula's city-states fall under the influence of a powerful, modernized country. Seeing this as the potential end of the peninsula's independence, Erica decides to fight for Stivale's dignity. Her battle to unify the Stivale Peninsula begins! Features: A classic RPG experience Explore a fantasy world Voiced characters New Game+ system Class change system Synthesis system Unique character abilities Sidequests Difficulty system
